'''Jammal-ud-Din Affendi''' (born 23 June 1908, date of death unknown) was an [[Afghanistan]] field hockey player, who competed at the [[1936 Summer Olympic Games]] and played in both games.<ref>[https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/af/jammal-ud-din-affendi-1.html Sports-Reference Profile] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528224415/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/af/jammal-ud-din-affendi-1.html |date=2015-05-28 }}</ref>

